Speaker 1: No problem. Yeah.

Speaker 1: Let me tell you what's new and improved about them.

Speaker 2: They work faster, they last longer,

Speaker 1: and they don't have the same side effects that a lot of people get with the

Speaker 2: other Viagras, like the dizziness and the headaches and even the stomach

Speaker 1: pains that some people do get.

Speaker 2: Right.

Speaker 1: But I'm not going to have you on a monthly program,

Speaker 2: but I just want to send you out 10 of these to try.

Speaker 1: What I'm going to do, I'm going to change your prescription so when you want

Speaker 2: to order, you'll get these going forward for when you do want to order.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 1: because I know our prices are going to go up drastically,

Speaker 2: you'll still be set in because you have a prescription on the file with this.

Speaker 1: All right, Jimmy, well, that sounds fair.

Speaker 2: So I won't be charged for this 10?

Speaker 1: No, you're not being charged for this 10.

Speaker 2: This is just for you to try.

Speaker 1: Well, thank you for letting me try it.

Speaker 2: I'm going to hold the prescription on file for six months.

Speaker 1: So that means you're not going to have any refills.

Speaker 2: So let us know by six months if you like these, if you want to order more,

Speaker 1: or if you just don't want to get any more at all.

Speaker 2: Okay, I will.

Speaker 1: Until you're ready to do that, okay?

Speaker 2: All right, that sounds fair enough.

Speaker 1: They're going to have the number 100 on the back.

Speaker 2: All right.
